-- use existing shipment_state_transitions_agg in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV0EQ1672167971204_shipment_state_transitions_agg
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "shipper_applications.name","shipper_shipment_agg.volume_rank_last_30_days") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY "shipper_shipment_agg.volume_rank_last_30_days" ASC, z__pivot_col_rank, "shipper_applications.name") AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "shipments.finance_record_month" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "shipments.finance_record_month") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(case
        when shipments.state='canceled' then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.shipper_application_id = 625 then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.is_tonu then coalesce((shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TONU_AT"), (coalesce(first_pickup_appointment.end_at::timestamp ,first_pickup_appointment.start_at::timestamp)))::timestamp_ntz
        else last_delivery.left_at::timestamp_ntz
      end
     AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM')) AS "shipments.finance_record_month",
    shipper_applications.name  AS "shipper_applications.name",
    coalesce(shipper_shipment_agg.rank,1000)  AS "shipper_shipment_agg.volume_rank_last_30_days",
    COALESCE(SUM(shipments.shipper_total_rate ), 0) AS "shipments.total_revenue_sum",
    COALESCE(SUM(( shipments.shipper_total_rate-(iff(shipments.carrier_application_id is null, null, shipments.carrier_total_rate))  ) ), 0) AS "shipments.total_margin_sum",
        COALESCE(SUM(( shipments.shipper_total_rate-(iff(shipments.carrier_application_id is null, null, shipments.carrier_total_rate))  ) ), 0) / nullif(COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN NOT (shipments.carrier_application_id  IS NULL) THEN shipments.shipper_total_rate  ELSE NULL END), 0), 0) AS "shipments.total_margin_percent_average",
    COALESCE(SUM(shipment_accessorials_agg.margin_sum ), 0) AS "shipment_accessorials_agg.accessorial_margin_sum"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV23I1672167977449_shipment_accessorials_agg AS shipment_accessorials_agg ON shipment_accessorials_agg.shipment_id=shipments.id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS first_pickup ON first_pickup.shipment_id=shipments.id and first_pickup.first_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(first_pickup.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stop_appointments  AS first_pickup_appointment ON first_pickup_appointment.shipment_stop_id=first_pickup.id and NOT ((TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(first_pickup_appointment.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) is not null)
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS last_delivery ON last_delivery.shipment_id=shipments.id and last_delivery.last_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON shipper_applications.id = shipments.shipper_application_id
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVHHT1672099916046_shipper_shipment_agg AS shipper_shipment_agg ON shipper_shipment_agg.id = shipper_applications.id
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV0EQ1672167971204_shipment_state_transitions_agg AS shipment_state_transitions_agg ON shipment_state_transitions_agg.shipment_id=shipments.id
WHERE ((( case
        when shipments.state='canceled' then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.shipper_application_id = 625 then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.is_tonu then coalesce((shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TONU_AT"), (coalesce(first_pickup_appointment.end_at::timestamp ,first_pickup_appointment.start_at::timestamp)))::timestamp_ntz
        else last_delivery.left_at::timestamp_ntz
      end
     ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( case
        when shipments.state='canceled' then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.shipper_application_id = 625 then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.is_tonu then coalesce((shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TONU_AT"), (coalesce(first_pickup_appointment.end_at::timestamp ,first_pickup_appointment.start_at::timestamp)))::timestamp_ntz
        else last_delivery.left_at::timestamp_ntz
      end
     ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 6, DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(case
        when shipments.state='canceled' then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.shipper_application_id = 625 then null::timestamp_ntz
        when shipments.is_tonu then coalesce((shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TONU_AT"), (coalesce(first_pickup_appointment.end_at::timestamp ,first_pickup_appointment.start_at::timestamp)))::timestamp_ntz
        else last_delivery.left_at::timestamp_ntz
      end
     AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    2,
    3) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 20 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank
